tps://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578160/extras/dbbbddcabecd722b4b76ecc30324705e.webp?t=1724766020\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578160/extras/dbbbddcabecd722b4b76ecc30324705e.poster.avif?t=1724766020\" class=\"bb_img\" width=600 height=39 /></picture></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578160/extras/02f9b5a93825c4b182c395d038605443.poster.avif?t=1724766020\" width=600 height=174 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578160/extras/02f9b5a93825c4b182c395d038605443.webm?t=1724766020\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1578160/extras/02f9b5a93825c4b182c395d038605443.mp4?t=1724766020\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 40 uniquely challenging platformer levels<br></li><li>Endless challenges and puzzles thanks to the game’s inbuilt level editor and level sharing<br></li><li>Levels feature additional mechanics such as grappling hook, speed boosters, conveyor belts and more<br></li><li>The bots follow your orders to the letter, no matter how stupid they are<br></li><li>Infinite supply of bots!</li></ul>",
